pageContext.claim: “And, by the way, Hispanic Americans just set a record for new jobs. African Americans just set a record for new jobs just now -- during the pandemic, the last month. And Asian Americans just set a record for new jobs. So we're very proud of what's happening.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump’s boasts about record job increases ignore the fact that these are not new job gains. Only jobs that have been recovered since the start of the pandemic. Overall, fewer people are employed now than when Trump was elected.
